Pre-Game Insights: Dejounte Murray was questionable against the Wizards with elbow soreness, but is now available.
The former Seattle, Washington native has an incentive in his contract tied to playing 65 games this year. If he misses another game, he misses out on the bonus.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Jose Alvarado returned to action for the first time since November, giving the team a major emotional boost.
The Pelicans are just 1-15 this season away from the Smoothie King Center.
The Wizards list Saddiq Bey (knee) and Marvin Bagley III (knee) out for Sunday as they did for Friday.
